What are adverbs of frequency? How can you talk about your routine in French? In this French lesson, we first clarify what adverbs and adverbial phrases of frequency are. We then discuss the French adverbs of frequency along with their pronunciation. I then go on to tell you about my morning routine, in French, to illustrate how both adverbs and adverbial phrases of frequency are used in context. We then do a little reading / listening exercise, for you to see how many French adverbs of frequency (and adverbial phrases) you can find in the text.

